\textbf{Context-Aware News Recommender System}

\vspace{-1pt}

Built a personalized news recommendation system using NLP, implicit feedback, and session-based tracking logic.
\vspace{-1pt}
\begin{itemize}
\item Engineered a collaborative filtering model with contextual embeddings to personalize news feeds based on reading habits.
\item Preprocessed unstructured textual data with spaCy and TF-IDF to extract topics and keyword relevance for each article.
\item Designed session-based features to track sequential engagement and apply behavior-weighted ranking to recommendations.
\item Integrated Flask API for recommendation delivery and evaluated A/B test results using engagement performance metrics.
\end{itemize}

\textbf{Pharmaceutical Named Entity Recognition}

\vspace{-1pt}

Developed a spaCy-based NER system to extract dosage, drugs, and formats from pharma communication documents.
\vspace{-1pt}
\begin{itemize}
\item Trained custom NER models using spaCy to identify pharmaceutical entities with over 85\% entity-level precision recall.
\item Annotated training data using Prodigy and balanced labels through semi-supervised sampling for low-frequency classes.
\item Deployed inference pipeline using FastAPI to return parsed tokens and tagged labels for real-time document queries.
\item Implemented visual analytics dashboard with streamlit to monitor model outputs and user intervention accuracy rates.
\end{itemize}

